{"tid":1541010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"四大訴求？重建警隊啊dklm","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:35.000Z","uid":103635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4580193aa7cf7d78dc027993aa240db75ae1ba","tid":1541010,"uid":103635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"宜家仲鳩叫四大訴求 缺一不可？<br />\n7月我地已經叫緊五大訴求<br />\n依家9月先應承<strong>一</strong>樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你唔係收貨呀嘛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經過咗721 831 <br />\n<strong>千幾人被捕 無數人被徹底摧殘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">死左嘅人 爆咗嘅眼 係唔會生番</span><br />\n案底 係跟個嗰人一世<br />\n破相 傷殘 心理創傷 <br />\n係唔會完全復原</strong><br />\n你係到鳩叫四大訴求！？<br />\n對得住佢地嗎？<br />\n對得住良知嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n依家香港幾乎係個軍政府<br />\n只要警員 <del>睇你唔順超</del> 懷疑你犯罪<br />\n佢點扑點打點壓點爆你缸<br />\n都係<span style=\"color: red;\">合理武力</span>阿<br />\n<br />\n你估成立到調查委員會就解決到件事！？<br />\n鉛水事件查晒啲嘢出嚟<br />\n咪又係底層水喉匠孭飛<br />\n真係痴線，咁大件事高層可以乜事都冇<br />\n仲要攞埋銀紫荊<br />\n<br />\n你仲覺得四大訴求扭轉到局面？<br />\n一日見唔到高官問責，警隊大洗血<br />\n我哋仲點訓得著！！！？？？<br />\n個樣後生啲、喺連儂牆/示威附近經過<br />\n就要預咗要俾人扑壓追打斬呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">強烈要求</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤銷對義士的檢控<br />\n撤回暴動定性<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n徹查721 831 警官鄉黑<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">警隊問責 重建改革</span><br />\n全面落實雙普選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 其實我覺得要平民憤，最少要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">向所有受傷示威者賠償</span></strong>，但具體鋪陳文宣未諗好，小的墨水法律知識都唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.P.S. 至於詳細改革警隊相關案例可以睇下北愛、<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/07/26/patten-report-blue-print-of-police-reform/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2Fpatten-report-blue-print-of-police-reform%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=f90d8e61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/07/26/patten-report-blue-print-of-police-reform/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/simonshen.blog/2019/07/24/%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25B6%2593/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fsimonshen.blog%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F%2525E7%25258D%2525A8%2525E7%2525AB%25258B%2525E8%2525AA%2525BF%2525E6%25259F%2525A5%2525E5%25258F%25258A%2525E8%2525AD%2525A6%2525E6%252594%2525BF%2525E6%252594%2525B9%2525E9%25259D%2525A9%2525E6%252589%25258D%2525E6%252598%2525AF%2525E6%2525A0%2525B9%2525E6%25259C%2525AC%2525E5%252587%2525BA%2525E8%2525B7%2525AF%2525EF%2525B8%2525B0%2525E5%25258C%252597%2525E6%252584%25259B%2525E7%252588%2525BE%2525E8%252598%2525AD%2525E7%25259A%252584%2525E7%2525B6%252593%2Famp%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=39ea8f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/simonshen.blog/2019/07/24/%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%2598%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25B6%2593/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"90f6a6fd0720c50eeaafc2e69613e10ba161caf8","tid":1541010,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqCKJBg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqCKJBg.png&h=665f9ef8&s={SIZE}\